    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - 2 SPEED REAR AXLES: SPICER - CLEAN AND INSPECT - INSPECT
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="6">
        <title>INSPECT</title>
        <svcprocinfo>
            <para>Prior to reassembly, inspect parts for signs of excessive wear or damage. Replacement of these parts
                can prevent premature failure and costly downtime.
            </para>
        </svcprocinfo>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Bearings</title>
            <para>Bearing surfaces should be inspected for pitting, excessive wear, or overheating (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401514">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401514" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401514" filename="../figg14/G1401514.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 14. Check Bearing Surfaces</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Thrust Washers</title>
            <para>Inspect thrust washers for scoring and cracking (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401515">Figure 15</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401515" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401515" filename="../figg14/G1401515.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 15. Inspect Thrust Washers</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Gears</title>
            <para>Inspect gears for wear or damage. Replace gears that are pitted, scored, or worn (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401516">Figure 16</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401516" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401516" filename="../figg14/G1401516.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 16. Inspect Gears</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Shafts</title>
            <para>Inspect shafts for nicks or scores (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401517">Figure 17</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401517" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401517" filename="../figg14/G1401517.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="208px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 17. Inspect Shafts</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Splines</title>
            <para>Inspect all splines for wear, distortion from twisting, and cracking (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401518">Figure 18</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401518" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401518" filename="../figg14/G1401518.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 18. Inspect Splines</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Housings</title>
            <para>Inspect housing for stripped threads and bending fatigue (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401519">Figure 19</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401519" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401519" filename="../figg14/G1401519.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 19. Inspect Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
